---
title: Cannellini Bean Toasts with Roasted Broccolini
description: This dish is so quick and easy, it will become your go-to weeknight meal. Garlicky beans and sweet caramelized onions are topped with crumbly goats cheese, all over warm ciabatta. We served it with roasted broccollini.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54bfb3536ced6e78178b4567.jpg
